1467
02:10:21.840 --> 02:10:25.730
他躺在那里呻吟  向医疗兵求救
He was laying there just groaning and calling for a medic.

1468
02:10:27.040 --> 02:10:30.000
我从水壶里倒了些水
I took water from my canteen,

1469
02:10:30.000 --> 02:10:34.080
又拿了些绷带  帮他洗了脸
got some bandage, and I washed his face.

1470
02:10:34.160 --> 02:10:39.000
清洗过后  他的眼睛逐渐睁开
And when I... was washing his eyes, his eyes came open.

1471
02:10:39.080 --> 02:10:42.760
天  他一下就有精神了
Man, he just lit up.

1472
02:10:43.880 --> 02:10:47.800
他说  "我还以为我瞎了"
